                    <div class="tabs-content-left mw--515px">
                      <div class="tabs-content-svg"><img loading="lazy" src="/images/pages/why-formx-effortless_on_the_go_icon-01-instant.svg" alt=""/></div>
                      <h3 class="mb-0">Instant Gratification</h3>
                      <div>Capture a document, and instantly see the extracted data. Say goodbye to waiting and experience the speed of mobile processing.</div>
