      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA banner -->
  <div class="section product-section px-40 why-formx">
    <div class="card-xl full-width green-shape-bg">
      <div class="card-xl-vertical-wrap text-center">
        <div class="card-xl-content-wrap left half-width">
          <h2 class="card-xl-title color-white">Beyond Extraction: A Streamlined Workflow Starts with FormX.ai</h2>
          <div class="card-xl-description color-white pricing">FormX.ai isn't just about document extraction – it's about revolutionizing your entire document processing pipeline. We go beyond extractors or Intelligent Document Processing (IDP) by offering a comprehensive suite of tools, including the Mobile Scan SDK, Workspace, and even post-processing for smooth integration. FormX.ai ensures a smooth and efficient workflow, from document capture to data extraction and beyond.</div>
