                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slide testimonial w-slide">
              <div class="testimonial-slide card-xl-testimonial-wrap">
                <div class="card-xl-testimonial-icon"><img src="/images/pages/Group-1974.svg" loading="lazy" alt=""/></div>
                <div class="card-xl-testimonial why-formx">&quot;FormX.ai automated our reward program! It extracts customer data from receipts, boosting participation and revenue. Customers love the convenience, and our staff can focus on service.&quot;</div>
                <div class="card-xl-testimonial-author-wrap">
                  <div class="card-xl-testimonial-author-photo rounded"><img src="/images/pages/why-formx-result_02-MarkLee@2x.webp" loading="lazy" alt=""/></div>
                  <div class="card-xl-testimonial-author-info-wrap">
                    <div class="card-xl-testimonial-author-info-name testimonial-name">Mark Lee</div>
                    <div class="card-xl-testimonial-author-info-position">Central Mall, Manila</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slide testimonial w-slide">
              <div class="testimonial-slide card-xl-testimonial-wrap">
                <div class="card-xl-testimonial-icon"><img src="/images/pages/Group-1974.svg" loading="lazy" alt=""/></div>
                <div class="card-xl-testimonial why-formx">&quot;FormX.ai extracts data from bills &amp; receipts like a champ! It saves us time &amp; reduces errors in bookkeeping, allowing us to focus on financial analysis. Highly recommend!&quot;</div>
                <div class="card-xl-testimonial-author-wrap">
                  <div class="card-xl-testimonial-author-photo rounded"><img src="/images/pages/why-formx-result_03-DavidChen@2x.webp" loading="lazy" alt=""/></div>
                  <div class="card-xl-testimonial-author-info-wrap">
                    <div class="card-xl-testimonial-author-info-name testimonial-name">David Chen</div>
                    <div class="card-xl-testimonial-author-info-position">CPA, Taipei Accounting Services</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
